        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Midjourney remains a top overall AI image generator in 2026, with outstanding artistic quality, photorealism, and compositional depth. Its Version 7 model delivers cinematic results that outperform competitors for creative and design work."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Which AI image generator handles text in images best?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Ideogram is a top AI image generator for text rendering, achieving approximately 90% accuracy on text in images. It far outperforms Midjourney and DALL-E for creating posters, ads, logos, and social media graphics with legible embedded text."
