      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Is there a free AI image generator that's actually good?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Yes, Stable Diffusion is a completely free, open-source AI image generator that is extremely powerful. It offers unparalleled customization through fine-tuning, LoRAs, and ControlNet. DALL-E 3 is also available at no extra cost to ChatGPT Plus subscribers."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
