      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Is Midjourney better than DALL-E?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Midjourney produces higher artistic quality and photorealism. DALL-E 3 is easier to use and has better natural language understanding. For professional creative work, Midjourney wins. For quick, reliable results without learning prompt engineering, DALL-E is better."
      }
