    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Which AI image generator is cheapest?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Stable Diffusion is completely free (open-source, run locally). DALL-E 3 is included with ChatGPT Plus ($20/month). Ideogram offers a generous free tier. Recraft and Leonardo both have free tiers with daily credits. Midjourney starts at $10/month."
