<h2>1. Midjourney — 🏆 Editor's Choice</h2>
<p>Midjourney remains the gold standard for artistic AI image generation. Version 7 delivers stunning photorealism, cinematic lighting, and compositional depth that competitors struggle to match. Its Discord-based interface has a learning curve, but the output quality is worth it.</p>

<h3>Test Results</h3>
<p><strong>Prompt used:</strong> "A futuristic cyberpunk city at sunset with neon signs, flying cars, and rain-slicked streets — cinematic, 8K"</p>
<ul>
<li>Generation time: ~22 seconds</li>
<li>Prompt adherence: 9.5/10</li>
<li>Lighting: 9.8/10 — exceptional cinematic quality</li>
<li>Text rendering: 2/10 — traditional weakness</li>
<li>Facial consistency: 9/10 across multiple generations</li>
</ul>

<h3>Multi-Dimension Rating</h3>
<table>
<thead><tr><th>Overall</th><th>Image Quality</th><th>Speed</th><th>Ease of Use</th><th>Typography</th><th>Value</th></tr></thead>
